{"tid":2194354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"周梓樂離世 10 個月　老伯拭淚：一定幫你報仇","createTime":"2020-09-08T12:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T15:23:46.000Z","uid":206047,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"25a139104f058f222dbf1d91a60d1eedf245af28","tid":2194354,"uid":206047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"香港科技大學學生周梓樂離世 10 個月。有網民呼籲在今日晚上 8 時 09 分為周梓樂默哀，以及到將軍澳尚德停車場外獻花致意。入夜之後，陸續有市民停車場外的祭壇獻花及拜祭，大批警員在現場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n有拄著柺杖的老伯走到祭壇前，雙手合十微微鞠躬，他又一度抽出紙巾拭抹眼睛，悲慟地向著祭壇方向道：「我哋會幫你報仇，我哋一定會幫你報仇。」<br />\n<br />\nFrom 立場新聞"},{"pid":"978eac0525981cfb70e3051589e9f06d0f64f3bd","tid":2194354,"uid":206047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9c9ef6d7ae6830785aa69ebff39768d4a76ed0","tid":2194354,"uid":206047,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"其實很多老一輩都冇放棄"},{"pid":"c36608975eb6410aee2e0ae9c97fa58f4d695dcf","tid":2194354,"uid":206047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6110f4162018d3742e89dd58fcc4d1b342c88e0","tid":2194354,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fi